THE STORY

Now we all know el Padre Pawstrong, the first cat who landed on the moon, was the king of taco eating competitions. He even beat Catt Stonie, eating 6 tacos and 9 nachos more than him. Turns out, tacos are the perfect fuel source for Catstronauts headed to the moon. The dense calories and slow digesting queso, creates the perfect recipe needed for a trajectory to the moon.

Did somebody say Tequila? Oh yeah, Tacos and Tequila go like Cats and Catnip. We’re getting in touch with only the best distilleries to partner up, stay tuned for updates. Step aside Dog Julio.

Become a Crew Member

9% Transaction fee

8% of all TacoCat transactions is put back into our Food Vault, which is locked inside of PancakeSwap LP, feeding the homeless, hitchhiking cats along the ride. 1% Returned to holders as a small way to say thank you. Auto-liquidity will ensure high and stable fuel levels.

Maximum Transaction

Maximum Transaction will be implemented at launch, this will prevent Fat Cats from weighing down the flight. No Fat Cats allowed onboard.

Locked Liquidity

50% Locked for 6 months and the other 50% locked for 12 months. The liquidity will be returned to donators after these two periods. Thank you for hopping aboard TacoCats.

Become a Crew Member

  • Marketing campaign begins for Taco Cat Tequila

Q4 2021

  • Bottles of TacoCat Tequila will be airdropped
  • Get more lit than a recovering cat in Catnip Anonymous
